text: Chernovsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnoyarsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 60 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Ufa, 6 km from Krasny Yar. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Chernovsky, Republic of Bashkortostan
